OL,3,CRetirement boost for savers with plans
OL,4,Cto scoop up smaller pension pots
OL,6,FPeople could get a retirement savings
OL,7,Fboost from a pension consolidator to
OL,8,Fscoop up smaller pots that may
OL,9,Fotherwise become lost.
OL,11,FThere are now 13 million of these
OL,12,Fsmall pots, holding #1,000 or less,
OL,13,Fwith the number increasing by around
OL,14,Fone million a year, the Government
OL,15,Fsaid.
