OL,3,CRetirement boost for savers with plans
OL,4,Cto scoop up smaller pension pots
OL,6,FUnder reforms introduced as part of
OL,7,Fthe Pension Schemes Bill, each
OL,8,Findividual saver's small pots will be
OL,9,Fbrought together into one pension
OL,10,Fscheme. People will still have the
OL,11,Fright to opt out.
OL,13,FThe Government said the move will also
OL,14,Freduce admin costs for businesses.
