OL,3,CRetirement boost for savers with plans
OL,4,Cto scoop up smaller pension pots
OL,6,FPensions minister Torsten Bell said:
OL,7,F"There are now more small pension pots
OL,8,Fin the UK than pensioners ` raising
OL,9,Fcosts and hassle for workers trying to
OL,10,Ftrack their savings. It also costs the
OL,11,Fpensions industry hundreds of millions
OL,12,Fof pounds every year.
OL,14,F"We will automatically bring together
OL,15,Fpeople's small pots into one high
OL,16,Fperforming pension, reducing costs as
OL,17,Fwell as hassle for savers. In time
OL,18,Fthis could boost the pension of an
OL,19,Faverage earner by around #1,000."
