OL,3,CRetirement boost for savers with plans
OL,4,Cto scoop up smaller pension pots
OL,6,FZoe Alexander, director of policy and
OL,7,Fadvocacy at the Pensions and Lifetime
OL,8,FSavings Association (PLSA), said: "The
OL,9,Faccumulation of small pots creates
OL,10,Funnecessary cost and complexity for
OL,11,Fsavers and schemes alike. The PLSA has
OL,12,Fworked extensively with industry and
OL,13,Fthe DWP (Department for Work and
OL,14,FPensions) to propose solutions and
OL,15,Fsupports the model being proposed by
OL,16,Fthe Government."
