OL,3,CRetirement boost for savers with plans
OL,4,Cto scoop up smaller pension pots
OL,6,FRocio Concha, Which? director of
OL,7,Fpolicy and advocacy, said: "Which?
OL,8,Fcalled for the consolidation of small
OL,9,Fpots under #1,000 before the election,
OL,10,Fso we are delighted that the
OL,11,FGovernment is committing to doing
OL,12,Fthis."
OL,14,FGail Izat, workplace managing director
OL,15,Fat Standard Life, part of Phoenix
OL,16,FGroup, said: "The introduction of
OL,17,Fconsolidators that can administer
OL,18,Fthese pots effectively and invest them
OL,19,Fdynamically will be a step forward."
